headline: Coterra Energy Schedules Fourth-Quarter and Full Year 2025 Results Conference Call for Friday, February 27, 2026
summary: HOUSTON, January 29, 2026--Coterra Energy Inc. ("Coterra" or the "Company") (NYSE: CTRA) today announced it will host a conference call on Friday, February 27, 2026, at 9:00 AM CT (10:00 AM ET) to discuss its fourth-quarter and full year 2025 financial and operating results. The Company plans to announce fourth-quarter and full year 2025 results after the market closes on Thursday, February 26, 2026.

headline: Coterra and Devon reportedly in advanced merger talks
summary: Investing.com -- Coterra Energy Inc. and Devon Energy Corp. are in advanced discussions about a potential merger that could be announced in the coming days, according a Bloomberg report Thursday.

headline: CNX Resources Corporation. (CNX) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: CNX Resources (CNX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +70.00% and +12.39%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
